DESCRIPTION

A covetable Yves Saint Laurent silhouette, the Kate wallet-on-chain bag is crafted in chevron stitched metallic green grained leather which adds texture and dimension to the bag, featuring a black suede nterior and finished with gold-tone metal 'Yves Saint Laurent' logo hardware . The shoulder strap is detachable for carry as a clutch or wallet.

About the Brand
What Goes Around Comes Around, also known as WGACA, is a premier purveyor of pre-owned luxury accessories and apparel from around the world. For nearly 30 years, theyve elevated traditional secondhand shopping into a high-fashion experience. For WGACA, sourcing pre-owned luxury isnt just a business, its an art and a science. Their team of buyers travel the world, navigating a network of trusted sources and hand-selecting pieces by coveted fashion houses. WGACAs meticulous methods and commitment to sourcing the most exclusive styles enables them to offer unique pieces by iconic designers you wont find anywhere else. Their customers include celebrities, tastemakers, and vintage connoisseurs, who come in search of authentic, pre-owned luxury, plus a shopping experience that is like no other. WGACA guarantees authenticity of every item through their multi-tiered authentication process. WGACA is not an authorized reseller and is not affiliated with any of the brands they sell. WGACA maintains an independent authentication process that is not verified by brands.
